      "writtenOn": "2026-04-17T23:21:14Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Automatically add the sorted trait if `refs` is a `RefMap` instance? Or are you dropping that behavior on purpose?\n```suggestion\n\t\tthis.traits \u003d traits.clone();\n\n\t\tif (refs instanceof RefMap) {\n\t\t\tthis.refs \u003d refs.values();\n\t\t\tthis.traits.add(PackedRefsTrait.SORTED);\n\t\t} else if (!traits.contains(PackedRefsTrait.SORTED)) {\n\t\t\tthis.refs \u003d RefComparator.sort(refs.values());\n\t\t\tthis.traits.add(PackedRefsTrait.SORTED);\n\t\t} else {\n\t\t\tthis.refs \u003d refs.values();\n\t\t}\n```",
